<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l3">Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wellen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l4"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> kürcʒlıchen / <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun vnd mıt eẅch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l5">reden <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
